snippet.textDisplay: I know the chances of you reading this are slim but I have a few things I to say. First I don't have Endo I have PCOS so I understand 100% how you feel when people want to talk about your health as a woman and it's not their place so you go girl and keep your chin up and know your not alone. I finely came to terms last year after trying everything and making my health worse, that me and my husband would never have a baby and it still hurts but I know I will have an amazing life with my husband filled with my cows and dogs. So remember you are not alone that the women who know your pain have your back and support and love you!! As far as Nick saying it's a cash grab if you watched the whole video he does love it he just doesn't feel it's worth the price point. I get what he means I personally don't feel it's a cash grab but for the price, I can't justify it when I only use concealer, tint, and powder myself. Working in a man's profession I end up covered in dirt, mud, and grease so it never makes sense to get all glammed up. I would love to give the blendiful a try but like I said I can't justify the money in my book. Also, can I vote for a burgundy/plum pallet :D now that would be awesome!!!!!
